{"tid":1763962,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［玩到我瞓為止］如何活著離開這深山","createTime":"2019-11-30T17:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T00:10:16.000Z","uid":60500,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4b41c2f92551560912ea6677f376d0259210de1e","tid":1763962,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"「痛......」<br />\n林菲潔忍著頭痛睜開眼，眼前的世界卻是上下癲倒。對了，巴士衝出了馬路，掉下了山崖。幸好有綁安全帶，我才撿回一命嗎？<br />\n林菲潔解下安全帶，跌到上下翻轉的巴士頂上，放眼望去，都是攤在一邊流著血的乘客們。怎麼看都不像活著的樣子。<br />\n「嗚啊......」<br />\n總之，現在該怎麼辦呢⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\nA. 先離開巴士呼救<br />\nB. 確認是否有其他生還者<br />\nC. 報警求救<br />\n<br />\n以第一個回答為准 玩到4點左右"},{"pid":"3cdcbcd79e933d82e58ebd01e0b75b2a6a9b3e69","tid":1763962,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:54:15.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"f2782c4423c2fbe7829b0c57eb33462b80bf8f50","tid":1763962,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:54:16.000Z","msg":"有冇人黎玩"},{"pid":"c29f55e1e4537433e9a0200443daa78dc07a4bdb","tid":1763962,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:54:23.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"5081c62df1582c4ab7b3da7d79cbf60b03bd81c8","tid":1763962,"uid":158372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"a36c907ac027a70b3c98eb9ac6636586c7129dd9","tid":1763962,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3cdcbcd79e933d82e58ebd01e0b75b2a6a9b3e69","tid":1763962,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:54:15.000Z","msg":"B"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T17:59:09.000Z","msg":"不，雖然是午夜，但這巴士載著超過四十人，不可能只有我活著吧。<br />\n<br />\n「有人還活著嗎！快醒醒！」菲潔大喊。<br />\n<br />\n「啊......發生什麼事？」<br />\n一個躺在地上、OL打扮的大姐姐發出微弱的叫聲，菲潔趕緊過去扶起她。她的頭受傷了。<br />\n<br />\nA. 先帶她離開巴士<br />\nB. 繼續搜救生存者"},{"pid":"3e076a2619ad47783c3a8978ab7d7d0cdf176f87","tid":1763962,"uid":139080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a36c907ac027a70b3c98eb9a